  "original_title": "20,000\u0d9a \u0d85\u0dbd\u0dca\u0dbd\u0dc3\u0d9a\u0dca \u0d9c\u0dad\u0dca \u0db4\u0ddc\u0dbd\u0dd2\u0dc3\u0dca \u0dc3\u0dd0\u0dbb\u0dba\u0db1\u0dca \u0d85\u0dad\u0dca\u0d85\u0da9\u0d82\u0d9c\u0dd4\u0dc0\u0da7",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "The police sergeant who took a bribe of 20,000 was arrested",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Officers of the Bribery and Corruption Investigation Division arrested a police sergeant on duty at the Hatton Magistrate's Court yesterday afternoon (17th) in connection with an incident in which he allegedly accepted a bribe of Rs 20000 from the plaintiff in order to cooperate with a pending case in the Hatton Magistrate's Court.",
        "A suspect who was arrested by the Hatton police and presented to the court in connection with a misplaced credit card of a resident of Hatton area, the suspect sergeant demanded a bribe of Rs 50000 from the complainant saying that he would take the necessary measures to strictly implement the law. Officers of the Bribery and Corruption Investigation Division arrested the sergeant on the basis of a complaint made to the Corruption Investigation Division when he was given Rs.",
        "The arrested suspect sergeant is to be presented to Hatton Magistrate."
      ],
